{"tid":280495,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"寫「啲」寫做「尐」嘅人覺唔覺得好作狀？","createTime":"2017-06-12T06:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T02:04:07.000Z","uid":9997,"like":106,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f7de08958e2819398f0a49125e51decc82a8c5","tid":280495,"uid":9997,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:26:41.000Z","msg":"明明就係啲！你就懶係正字咁寫尐！錯字扮正字！<br />\n仲要話人地錯，自己先啱，真係好無知"},{"pid":"0283a20fd57955531642fefe83e278ab76773011","tid":280495,"uid":8028,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:28:43.000Z","msg":"尐"},{"pid":"dc101908302a7bfe7a2ffb81169b012372787dc5","tid":280495,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"多啲，少啲！好啲！正啲！靚啲！樣衰啲！"},{"pid":"c86f642f41fdca28660c8334d56cb1142845f0f4","tid":280495,"uid":9997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尐</blockquote><br />\n你好作狀呀"},{"pid":"dc6eee6858879b38c379e4a15c648d9b243c04de","tid":280495,"uid":34523,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"頭文字尐"},{"pid":"9fdc059322f9ca432f4bd8c7903f6794c223b432","tid":280495,"uid":67238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:33:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9啦 係撚讀啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B0%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B0%2590&d=dAB382t62nNZuTUV3w6BBb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=dbafdde8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B0%90</a>"},{"pid":"193122e7f64ec746ad85ffb5e023c016ef7e336e","tid":280495,"uid":67238,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"近年有人將「尐」呢個生僻字，講成係「啲」嘅本字或正字，原因係「尐」解作少，同「啲」（解作一點、一些）有相似嘅地方，更有專欄作家同報章評論員將佢誤傳。「啲」嘅讀音係di1，但「尐」嘅讀音係zit3，尐嘅反切係「子列切」，反切上字取聲母(子-&gt;zi-&gt;z)，下字取韻母(列-&gt;lit-&gt;it)，切出嚟嘅音就係zit，讀音都唔啱，所以無可能係本字或正字。而且意思唔係相同，例如「多啲」（多一點），如果寫成「多尐」就會變成（多少），意思已經唔同咗。"},{"pid":"edc36e62a74d055dcabe66557f03b15b3af6fd25","tid":280495,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近年有人將「尐」呢個生僻字，講成係「啲」嘅本字或正字，原因係「尐」解作少，同「啲」（解作一點、一些）有相似嘅地方，更有專欄作家同報章評論員將佢誤傳。「啲」嘅讀音係di1，但「尐」嘅讀音係zit3，尐嘅反切係「子列切」，反切上字取聲母(子-&gt;zi-&gt;z)，下字取韻母(列-&gt;lit-&gt;it)，切出嚟嘅音就係zit，讀音都唔啱，所以無可能係本字或正字。而且意思唔係相同，例如「多啲」（多一點），如果寫成「多尐」就會變成（多少），意思已經唔同咗。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己係中文系都見有唔少on9同學會用依個字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9925a5f0957550ea0b1ed7ca202364aa3ed454ce","tid":280495,"uid":54733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"中大：<br />\n<br />\n「啲」是方言詞，流行於粵語、客家話，表示少許、一點兒。<br />\n<br />\n　　「啲」有多種用法：用於形容詞後，表示少許，如「快啲」即快點兒，「少啲」即少一點兒。又表示不定的數量，相當於一些、若干，如「呢啲」即這些，「嗰啲」即那些，「邊啲」即哪些。又用於句首的名詞前，表示這些或哪些，如「啲海鮮好生猛」即那些海鮮活蹦亂跳（形容很新鮮的樣子）。<br />\n<br />\n　　粵語「啲咑」即嗩吶，「啲咑」（粵音di1 da4，普通話di1 da2）模擬嗩吶發出的樂音，故又可表示嗩吶聲，「啲咑」多用於紅事和白事（指嫁娶喪葬之事）；「啲咑佬」即吹嗩吶的人、吹鼓手。明代胡文煥《群音類選》諸腔類卷四：「臘月初八，分付梅香洒掃廳堂，懸掛起古盡，烹起些滚茶，鼓兒打得鼕鼕，板兒打得呷呷，吹起喇吧鎖呐，喇吧吹得嘻嘻哽嗄，鎖呐吹得啲啲咑咑，笛兒吹得嚌嚌喳喳。」<br />\n<br />\n　　俗語「大唔大嘥啲吖」表示未免有點太浪費了。而「冇啲定性」（或作「冇喱定性」）表示沒有一點兒安定，形容不能安坐、不穩重、不踏實。「逐啲」表示逐步地、一點一點地。「一啲啲咁多」表示一點點兒。「一啲啲喇」表示各自的情況不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=啲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-mf%2Fsearch.php%3Fword%3D%E5%95%B2&d=dAB382t62nNZuTUV3w6BBb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=9030dc57\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=啲</a>"},{"pid":"6d81e5ead5b2fa79d563103c5200c209b324a997","tid":280495,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪撚on9啦 係撚讀啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B0%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B0%2590&d=dAB382t62nNZuTUV3w6BBb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=dbafdde8\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B0%90</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗰啲人真係懶醒！"},{"pid":"6de4d55311a32e9b0c4dfe6eacc19dd838e4495a","tid":280495,"uid":24623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:42:44.000Z","msg":"寫口語又要扮晒野寫正字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寫尐仲衰過寫5p字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe0c5323bc858f2cdabdf56d1e5be4c4eac54ba","tid":280495,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>近年有人將「尐」呢個生僻字，講成係「啲」嘅本字或正字，原因係「尐」解作少，同「啲」（解作一點、一些）有相似嘅地方，更有專欄作家同報章評論員將佢誤傳。「啲」嘅讀音係di1，但「尐」嘅讀音係zit3，尐嘅反切係「子列切」，反切上字取聲母(子-&gt;zi-&gt;z)，下字取韻母(列-&gt;lit-&gt;it)，切出嚟嘅音就係zit，讀音都唔啱，所以無可能係本字或正字。而且意思唔係相同，例如「多啲」（多一點），如果寫成「多尐」就會變成（多少），意思已經唔同咗。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己係中文系都見有唔少on9同學會用依個字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一早知讀zit 係on9仔讀d音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01d52c8e362a2e12c419980b961f5f6784f71ef","tid":280495,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:43:57.000Z","msg":"見人用又跟風用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常都係戇鳩仔黎"},{"pid":"69c7b37000e7694154c7f8357a877d641e86383c","tid":280495,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"<bl